Class ServiceChannel

java.lang.Object
com.iunera.jsonldjava.schemaorg.metadatatypes.Thing
com.iunera.jsonldjava.schemaorg.metadatatypes.Intangible
com.iunera.jsonldjava.schemaorg.metadatatypes.ServiceChannel
public class ServiceChannel extends Intangible
A means for accessing a service, e.g. a government office location, web site, or phone number.
